text: TransAsia Airways (TNA; ) is an airline based in the Neihu District, Taipei, Taiwan. It was the first private civil airline in Taiwan. it used to fly to Southeast and East Asia in November 2016 Trans Asia suspended and ceased all its operations due to 2 hull losses However V Air the low cost subsidiary ceased operations a month before in october 2016 ==Related pages== *TransAsia Airways Flight 222 ==References== == Other websites == *TransAsia Airways *TransAsia Airways Korea Category:Airlines of Taiwan
